channel.description:
hello guys and welcome to my thread. This Server is going to be a Spawn/Eco meaning that you cant Spawn every item there is. You need to save up for the good items, + i am working on a money system that you need to buy everything with cash. There will be a PvP zone that i am working on at the moment, and wild, I am planning on making that you dont lose items if you die in the wilderness but you gain PvP drops so you can sell your items. Enough of the Explaining, I will add featuures soon but here are pics

item.dc:creator: @Team_Rocket Team_Rocket
item.description:
@Team_Rocket wrote:

I was trying to be nice, and give you constructive feedback to help you. Now I’m going to give you my honest opinion; since you’re determined to be an ass. I’m sure 90% of MoparScape will share my view - as usual.

There is absolutely nothing unique, noteworthy, or outstanding in your Source. You have barely done anything by yourself, and this is if you didn’t rip your ‘Spawning System’ out of another Base. Your Korasi Special Attack looks like shit, and is poorly done. I’d love to know how you “ripped it straight from runescape” like you have access to something which we don’t. Your Inventory Models are terrible. Also, you can’t even figure out how to reset your Stand Animation. I doubt this will get very far, if it even makes it off the ground.

P.S. Act like a prick and I promise you I’ll be the bigger prick.
